Privacy Policy
Effective Date:
5 October 2023
Thank you for choosing Taptool, the mobile app builder for Shopify stores. At Taptool, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your data. This Privacy Policy outlines the information we collect, how it is used, and the measures we take to safeguard your data.
Information We Collect
1. App Logs and Crash Data
: We collect app logs and crash data to monitor the performance of our app and identify and resolve technical issues.
2. Shopify Store Data
: To create native mobile components and ensure a seamless experience, we may collect Shopify store data, including layout and product information. This data is used solely for app building purposes.
3. Data Required for App Deployment
: To facilitate iOS and Android app deployment, we may collect data related to your app configuration and requirements. This data is necessary to create and publish your app on app stores.
Data Handling
No Personal Data Storage
: Taptool does not store any personal data. We do not collect or retain information such as names, addresses, phone numbers, or email addresses.
On-Device Processing
: Any personal data that is processed during app creation is done exclusively on the userâ€™s device. We do not transmit personal data to our servers.
Data Security
We take data security seriously and implement stringent measures to protect your information:
Encryption
: Data transmission is encrypted to safeguard your information during transfer.
Access Control
: Access to your data is restricted to authorized personnel only.
Data Retention
: We retain data for the minimum time required to achieve the purposes for which it was collected.
Your Consent
By using the Taptool app builder, you consent to the collection and use of data as described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with this policy, please refrain from using our services.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
Taptool reserves the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the updated policy on our website or within the app. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the data we collect, please contact us at
contact@taptool.com
